songs.title: I Don’t Sell Molly
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Savage Tay on the beat
Oh yeah, in this ho

[Chorus]
I got the gas and the coke
I don't sell molly no more
I got the white, and the green
And it gotta be a pint if you lookin' for the lean

[Verse]
Savage Tay's trap status on El Chapo
And I feed your girl, mix the molly in dem' tacos
And my niggas crazy, El Loco on mi Laco
And when we come through all you hear is grra-po (grr-apo)
And we pop up

[Outro]
Yeah, stacks on that money game boy, yeah
